title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Try to export the data in the table.

Observed Behavior: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.

Expected Behavior: The data should be exported successfully.
OB: An exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method when attempting to export data from the table containing highlight/map in the attached report.
EB: When attempting to export the data from the table containing highlight/map in the attached report, the data should be exported successfully.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Try to export the data in the table.
